s-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/31\/2022\/03\/1-1-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/31\/2022\/03\/1-1-300x199.jpg 300w, https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/31\/2022\/03\/1-1-768x511.jpg 768w, https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/31\/2022\/03\/1-1.jpg 1092w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/no-longer-looking-for-love-you-are-not-alone\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"99\">No Longer Looking For Love? You Are Not Alone.&nbsp;<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As the pandemic reshaped our conception of love and relationships, the words of American author bell hooks are more prevalent than ever. &nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/category\/culture\/\">Culture<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator alignwide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><a href=\"https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/the-other-side-of-dawn-london-photo-story\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/31\/2022\/03\/2-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-513 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/31\/2022\/03\/2-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/31\/2022\/03\/2-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/31\/2022\/03\/2-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/31\/2022\/03\/2-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/31\/2022\/03\/2-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/31\/2022\/03\/2-1600x1200.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/31\/2022\/03\/2-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/31\/2022\/03\/2-1980x1485.jpg 1980w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/the-other-side-of-dawn-london-photo-story\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"137\">The &#8216;Other&#8217; Side of Dawn London &#8211; Photo Story<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Who is in the street in the dead of night? Who are these people that are, in a factual sense, unseen by most people? What are they doing?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/category\/identity\/\">Idenity<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator alignwide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><a href=\"https:\/\/mccs-journalism.gold.ac.uk\/wp\/blurr\/from-taboo-to-spectacle-a-history-of-lgbtq-representation-in-film\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"102